title: <span style="color: #000000;">**Wirth**</span> Government unstable..
subtitle: The opposition cannot be ignored any longer..
new-page: true
tags: event
view-if: year == 1922 and month == 11 and spd_in_government = 1 and chancellor == "Wirth"
max-visits: 1
